            <p><span style="color:#0070C0"><b>Annex C - Progress of Bill Table</b></span></p>
            <blockContainer>
              <num>69 </num>
              <p><span style="color:#000000">This Annex shows how each section and Schedule of the Act was numbered during the passage of the Bill through Parliament. </span></p>
